      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个图，说明实验室里怎么用Linux环境把本地NFS数据同步到Azure Files。核心场景是On-Prem Linux服务器，上面挂了一个NFS Share /data。",
      "elements_involved": [
